%!PS-Adobe-3.0 EPSF-3.0
%%BoundingBox: 0 0 300 250
%%EndComments
% Two rows with uneven vertical spacing
0 0 0 setrgbcolor
newpath  60  50 20 0 360 arc fill
newpath 150  50 20 0 360 arc fill
newpath 240  50 20 0 360 arc fill
newpath  60 180 20 0 360 arc fill
newpath 150 180 20 0 360 arc fill
newpath 240 180 20 0 360 arc fill
showpage
%%EOF
